          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-surface-2 flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/expert-approvals.svg" alt="Human approving a proposed action" class="w-full border-b border-line bg-surface-3" style="height: 160px; object-fit: cover;">
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="text-fg-1 text-base font-medium">Controlled by expert approvals</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-fg-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">Tool use, integrations, and high-impact actions stay inside approval boundaries your operators define.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
